  <brief_title>Timely Detection of Treatment Emergent Serious and Non-serious Adverse Events for Saxenda® in Mexican Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Timely Detection of Treatment Emergent Serious and Non-serious Adverse Events for Saxenda® in Mexican Patients</official_title>
