  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in North America. The aim is to investigate timely detection of
      pancreatitis cases as well as cases of suspicion of serious and non-serious adverse reactions
      possibly or probably related to Saxenda® in Mexican patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
